{"tid":1067851,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"油麻地男子墮樓亡　假牙飛脫","createTime":"2019-03-18T23:26:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-19T00:20:50.000Z","uid":41404,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"c8840bee351fbb5cc764745fb9e8b1acea10bd86","tid":1067851,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T23:26:52.000Z","msg":"今日(19日)凌晨5時許，一名50餘歲男子，被發現由油麻地利業街15號萬安樓墮下，倒臥行人路，頭部重創昏迷，途人報警，救護員到場將事主送院搶救，惜返魂乏術。警員調查後，相信事主由天台墮下，在地上發現屬於他的一副假牙，現正跟進墮樓原因。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190319/mobile/bkn-20190319060624644-0319_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190319%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20190319060624644-0319_00822_001.html&d=%2FQX5ewQS1riptUQ52WFoKm0Q%2Fwx8zutUsTDhO6XOofs%3D&h=161ffa72\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190319/mobile/bkn-20190319060624644-0319_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"a2b88957970e63279e7f77c6251fcd125b33e3d2","tid":1067851,"uid":178800,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T23:27:48.000Z","msg":"G殺"},{"pid":"c331512071dfc082dd8a2bc304fda3473667ac66","tid":1067851,"uid":3302,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T23:27:57.000Z","msg":"拾取物品:廢老的假牙"},{"pid":"8c77c97f9145187dab614fa46510c347a1f6f055","tid":1067851,"uid":17622,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T23:28:15.000Z","msg":"用保麗淨咪冇事。<br />\nR.I.P."},{"pid":"b6df046dc6205e905e98815a2d7a0da5d62de181","tid":1067851,"uid":28510,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T23:29:57.000Z","msg":"百變星君"},{"pid":"c405fab3cbf2469114cbcf52a621f8f32be7116c","tid":1067851,"uid":76710,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T23:32:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://forum.hkgolden.com/icons/305.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.hkgolden.com%2Ficons%2F305.gif&h=faa53cc7&s={SIZE}\